ORC Licensed Material
---------------------

rustChip is primarily an NPU driver and neuromorphic computing tool.
The ORC layer has limited direct applicability but covers mechanical
interactions produced by or in conjunction with rustChip:

  - NPU compute dispatch patterns used for game simulation mechanics
    (e.g. spiking neural network inference applied to encounter math,
    reservoir computing for procedural generation)
  - Inference pipeline patterns when used as game-rule engines
    (e.g. neuromorphic classification for NPC behavior trees,
    ensemble NPU voting for probabilistic game outcomes)
  - Hardware/software benchmark methodologies when codified as
    reproducible mechanical interactions

